With some help from telegram friends, i managed to solve my own problem. The problem is that i only shallow copied `result` which is `List&lt;List&lt;Integer&gt;&gt;` when i put the value into memo.

Deep copying is required for `List&lt;List&lt;Integer&gt;&gt;`.   

Shallow copy: `memo.put(target, new ArrayList&lt;&gt;(temp));`

Deep copy : `memo.put(target, new ArrayList&lt;&gt;( temp.stream().map(ArrayList::new).collect(Collectors.toList()) ));`   

Do remember to deep copy when you are returning value from memo also.

